{
  "stem": "812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And business was good, until the Germans took over, and we were forced to sell our home and our business for very little money.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And, of course, then everything was lost.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we then, by way of Hanover, went to Holland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] In Holland, we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my parents were asked to settle in Gouda.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That's Gouda.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there they were assigned to take care of some 125 children whose parents sent them from various parts of Europe-- Europe to [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] save them from the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my parents took care of these children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that was from the beginning of '39 until-- about April of '39, I believe, until the end of '39.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] shortly thereafter, we were to-- actually, our plans and our papers were all ready to immigrate to-- to America, and that was to be in May of 1940.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Our number was constantly set back, and this was, I'm sorry to say, due to the American State Department.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We were always set back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were supposed to leave in-- in May, and then it was set back another week or two and then more and more set back, until finally the Germans invaded Holland.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then it was too late for us to leave, and we were trapped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In the interim, of course, all of our belongings, which were on board ship in Rotterdam, were completely destroyed as the harbor of Rotterdam was bombed by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I, at the age of four, had my trousseau packed already, because we, as I said, we did have the moneys in Germany.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we had lifts packed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Lifts are huge containers.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
